Package rocks.xmpp.extensions.softwareinfo

Class SoftwareInformation

  • java.lang.Object
    • rocks.xmpp.extensions.softwareinfo.SoftwareInformation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    StandardizedDataForm, SoftwareInfo
    public final class SoftwareInformation
extends Object
implements StandardizedDataForm, SoftwareInfo
    Represents a view of the standardized fields of the 'urn:xmpp:dataforms:softwareinfo' data form to be included in service discovery responses to provide detailed information about the software.

    This class is immutable.

    See Also:
    5.1 Field Standardization
